## D25 Wiki Knowledge Layer — Storage, RAG, and Agent Tools
**Status:** proposed
**Depends on:** G18, A10

### Data Model

```rust
struct WikiPage {
    id: String,              // slug: "stm32f4-register-map"
    title: String,
    content: String,         // LLM-compressed markdown (5-10 pages)
    source_type: WikiSource,  // Manual, Guide, ApiRef, Custom
    source_ref: Option<String>, // original PDF/filename
    tags: Vec<String>,
    embedding: Option<Vec<f32>>, // pre-computed vector
    created_at: u64,
    updated_at: u64,
    version: u32,
}

enum WikiSource { Manual, Guide, ApiRef, Custom }
```

### Storage Layout

```
{project}/
├── specs/          # existing specs
└── wiki/
    ├── manifest.json    # page index + metadata
    ├── stm32f4-register-map.md
    ├── harness-setup-guide.md
    └── ...
```

### Agent Tools

| Tool | Description | Profession Access |
|---|---|---|
| `query_wiki` | Semantic search: query → top-K passages via vector similarity | All professions |
| `create_wiki_page` | Create new page with markdown content | Coder, Documenter |
| `update_wiki_page` | Update existing page content | Coder, Documenter |
| `list_wiki` | List all wiki pages with metadata | All professions |

### RAG Pipeline

1. **Indexing**: On wiki page create/update, compute embedding via local model or API
2. **Query**: Agent calls `query_wiki("timer register configuration")` → vector similarity search → top 3-5 passages returned
3. **Token budget**: Each retrieval returns ≤500 tokens (vs ~4000 for full manual page)

### UI: Wiki Tab

- Left column `Wiki` tab alongside `Chats` and `Specs`
- GitBook-style rendering: sidebar TOC + content area + metadata panel
- Full-text search bar + semantic search
- Markdown editor with live preview for page editing
